metadata.name: Flowing With Fire
metadata.description:
How does the gypsy play with fire and not get burnt?
She makes it a part of her, owns it. 
Until it flows out as an extension of her will. 

This artwork was developed digitally using mixed techniques, starting from videomaking, selecting frames, coloring the shot, and digitally painting to bring the vision to life.

Artwork and Copyright: Fer Caggiano
Writing: David Clark
Gypsy: The Zebra
